222
00:17:53,030 --> 00:17:55,949
Do you know that my boss is dead?

223
00:17:56,033 --> 00:17:57,826
You mean, Kang Yong-tak?

224
00:17:57,910 --> 00:18:00,996
Don't you think
they're the ones who did it?

225
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:03,749
LIM IN-GWAN

226
00:18:10,422 --> 00:18:14,426
I don't care if the Haegol Gang,
Youngjin Sect or the senator did it.

227
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,844
All I care about

228
00:18:16,470 --> 00:18:20,307
