236
00:18:57,302 --> 00:18:59,471
She only thought about using me to escape.

237
00:19:01,473 --> 00:19:04,768
That's the story of my life.
I never had a real friend.

238
00:19:04,852 --> 00:19:06,812
People have always tried to use me.

239
00:19:07,396 --> 00:19:10,023
But I know why.
Because I don't have strength.

240
00:19:10,107 --> 00:19:11,942
