256
00:20:44,368 --> 00:20:48,580
Yeah. It would be quiet here
even during lunch recess.

257
00:20:49,331 --> 00:20:52,000
Sometimes, I would come
and eat my lunch here alone.

258
00:21:01,176 --> 00:21:02,344
I have something to tell you.

259
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,263
I

260
